Package: apeglm
Title: Approximate posterior estimation for GLM coefficients
Version: 0.99.10
Author: Anqi Zhu, Joseph G. Ibrahim, Michael I. Love
Maintainer: Anqi Zhu <anqizhu@live.unc.edu>
Description: apeglm provides Bayesian shrinkage estimators for effect sizes for a variety of GLM models, using approximation of the posterior for individual coefficients.
VignetteBuilder: knitr
Imports: emdbook, SummarizedExperiment, GenomicRanges, methods, stats, utils
Suggests: DESeq2, airway, BiocStyle, knitr, rmarkdown, testthat
License: GPL-2
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
biocViews: Sequencing, RNASeq, DifferentialExpression, GeneExpression, Bayesian
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
